Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:39.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏過所有的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:43.81,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
