Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.91,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手無策 在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.91,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投無路 遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:02.50,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己鏡中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.34,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:13.96,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:20.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告別 這種答案毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:25.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:29.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:23.02,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行屍走肉般走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:28.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}頭頂的陽光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何時你已經淪落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:39.45,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}連自己名字也都遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:43.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:47.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:51.24,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如隨之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:56.94,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:08.36,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}從寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 聽風帶來山林的迴響
